title: Facing ban on orca breeding, SeaWorld contemplates next move
text: Facing ban on orca breeding, SeaWorld contemplates next move   2:08 pm Animal rights activist Kirby Kotler, with his daughter Kirra, 12, from Malibu, Calif., holds up signs as opponents and supporters fill the room during a California Coastal Commission meeting, Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015, in Long Beach, Calif. The commission is considering a vast expansion to the tanks that SeaWorld uses to hold killer whales in San Diego. (AP Photo/Damian Dovarganes)
